metadata.othernotes:
This version of Nadeshiko is meant to portray the character in her college years, in-between the end of the current anime, and the movie. I have intended to portray her around the age of 19-20, as a young, energetic, spunky, but friendly young woman with a fiery passion for the great outdoors.

SEXUAL PREFERENCES:
Nadeshiko is portrayed here as bisexual. While Nadeshiko has a traditional horniess towards guys, she gets all "naughty and excited" so-to-speak towards females. Nadeshiko is a very honest character, and isn't afraid to show how she might feel in certain situations. She finds the difference in things like penis size and boob size very interesting, but doesn't have a favorite size persay.

TIPS FOR INTERACTIONS:
-Yuru Camp is an anime that takes place in the real world, without any fantastical elements. As such, Nadeshiko doesn't have much experience with things like magic and superheroes, having believed such things to be fictional. It's also likely that she might not be familiar with certain properties or franchises, so Nadeshiko would definitely be keen to learn more.

-Depending on what your character is like, Nadeshiko's reaction may differ. While she's happy and friendly with most characters, more intimating characters might scare her a little. For these more intimidating characters, how you act towards her in targets will affect whether she warms up to your character, or still feels intimidated by them.

-Bringing up camping in any capacity is a surefire way to get Nadeshiko talking. If you prompt her, she'll be more than happy to ramble about camping (which she already does), but is willing to provide some tips if you ask her.

-Food is another favorite topic of Nadeshiko. Nadeshiko's not only a big eater, but a really good cook, especially while camping. Suggesting foods for her to make or try later, or interesting cooking techniques for her to give a try later.

case.name: Partner Appeal
case.description: Nadeshiko asks the table a simple question: what do they prefer in a partner? Looks or Personality? She also hints at a possible relationship with someone, which you can prompt her to talk about.

case.name: Nadeshiko's Camping Tips
case.description: Nadeshiko will give the other players a selection of camping tips, ranging from how to get started, to cooking meals.

case.name: Accesory Questions (Male)
case.description: Nadeshiko asks the other characters some questions. Use the tags to repsond to them.

case.name: Accesory Questions (Female)
case.description: Nadeshiko asks the other characters some questions. Use the tags to repsond to them.

case.name: Nadeshiko the Cook
case.description: Nadeshiko reveals to the other players she's a good cook. This could be a good time for characters with the chef tag to talk about their cooking experiences with Nadeshiko.

case.name: Specials
case.description: Nadeshiko asks the table what sort of specials are offered at the Inventory on a certain day of the week.

case.name: Need a Friend?
case.description: Nadeshiko offers her friendship to a character with the "lonely" tag.

case.name: Interesting Stories
case.description: Nadeshiko asks the table about some interesting stories, as a way to get to know the table better.

case.name: So...Where are We?
case.description: Nadeshiko asks how they're all here together, as everyone at the table came from a wide variety of places.
